the exterior of via verde showing off its stepped roofby john martinfor people old enough to remember it s hard to believe how far the bronx has come since the and the south bronx lost over residents as crime spiked and people made way for the suburbs .
the borough became synonymous with urban decay a stigma it continues to fight decades after it began its dramatic reboundtoday the bronx is flourishing as the public and private sectors continue to make the borough a healthier and more pleasant place to live .
it s hard to find a better example of how far the borough has come than via the mixedincome housing development in the melrose neighborhood that opened in .
since then it has earned international acclaim for its bold design and its focus on creating a green urban environment for its residentsthe project which sits on a cleanedup former rail yard provides units of living space views of the manhattan skyline and healthyliving amenities galore .
a string of green roofs dot the building s terraces as do solar panels which provide electricity to all the building s common spaces .
residents have access to shared gardening beds a children s playground a fitness center and an outdoor amphitheater .
throw in the building s easy access to subway and bus lines and it becomes easy to understand why via verde has been held up as a model for environmentally sustainable developmentas of today we can add the epa to the list of those who have officially recognized via verde s accomplishments .
this morning the epa announced that via verde received an honorable mention for the national award for smart growth achievement in the category of built projects .
of the smart growth achievement applications the epa received from across the country via verde was just one of seven to be recognizedfor a borough that has come so far and fought so long to create livable thriving communities via verde is a crowning achievement and an inspiration to urban areas everywhereto read more about via verde and the other projects receiving national award for smart growth achievement visit http wwwepagovsmartgrowthawardshtmeditor s note the views expressed here are intended to explain epa policy .
