six steps closer to a sustainable worldby dr alan d hecht addressing the problems of the century will require a combination of strategies including creative use of existing environmental policies and regulations innovative application of science and technology and collaboration among stakeholders read the postabout the author dr alan hecht is director for sustainable development office of research and development at the us environmental protection agency epa .
